data.description: A Modest Great Starter Home or a Vacation Getaway. Come see this wonderful Place with a peaceful running stream in the back yard. A Large Living room with the perfect window seating and a Modern Pellet stove to keep you extra warm on a chilly Pocono Night. They know the next owner will appreciate the love and care that has been put into special place.  Lots of space inside and out,,, with a 3 season screened porch,Also including a Detached Garage with a loft. Many amenities, With a Pool,Lake and clubhouse. Central sewer ,Well Water,  Low Taxes ,Your affordable Pocono living ,
